title: Elise Stefanik Believes She Can Turn New York  Into a Republican State
description: Ms. Stefanik, who leads the House Republican Conference, represents a hard right turn from New York’s tradition of so-called Rockefeller Republicanism.
dc:creator: Jesse McKinley
media:credit: Cindy Schultz for The New York Times
media:description: Representative Elise Stefanik predicts that the Republican Party will win a majority of New York’s 26 House seats in November.
